## Data and Privacy

Users of this software are responsible for:

- Complying with local data protection and privacy laws
- Implementing appropriate security measures for user data
- Obtaining necessary consents for data collection and processing
- Ensuring secure transmission and storage of sensitive information
- Regular security audits and updates

